Description: OTA Update Client for FoundriesFactory™
 A command-line utility for performing over-the-air (OTA) updates of
 Compose Apps built and managed through FoundriesFactory™. It provides
 a secure and reliable mechanism to fetch and install updates on
 devices running containerized applications.
